{"General": {"Code": "2519", "Type": "Common Stock", "Name": "AuGrp (Shenzhen) Cross-Border", "Exchange": "HK", "CurrencyCode": "HKD", "CurrencyName": "Hong Kong Dollar", "CurrencySymbol": "HK$", "CountryName": "Hong Kong", "CountryISO": "HK", "OpenFigi": "BBG01QKP0WR3", "ISIN": null, "LEI": null, "PrimaryTicker": null, "CIK": null, "EmployerIdNumber": null, "FiscalYearEnd": "December", "IPODate": null, "InternationalDomestic": null, "Sector": "Consumer Cyclical", "Industry": "Furnishings, Fixtures & Appliances", "GicSector": null, "GicGroup": null, "GicIndustry": null, "GicSubIndustry": null, "Description": "AuGroup (SHENZHEN) Cross-Border Business Co., Ltd. operates as an online retailer for furniture and home furnishings in the People's Republic of China, the United States, Other North American countries, other European countries Germany, and internationally. The company offers furniture and home furnishings, consisting of beds, bookcases, dressers, chests of drawers, vanity tables and vanity benches, food cabinets, sideboards, sofas, and outdoor furniture; electric tools, such as power screwdrivers, air pumps, jump starters, and car vacuums; home appliances comprising refrigerators and juicers; and consumer electronics, including power banks, chargers, and cables. It also provides logistics solutions, including warehousing, express and freight delivery, and related value-added services.It offers its products under the ALLEWIE, IRONCK, LIKIMIO, SHA CERLIN, HOSTACK, and FOTOSOK brand names. The company was formerly known as AuGroup Technology Co., Ltd. and changed its name to AuGroup (SHENZHEN) Cross-Border Business Co., Ltd. in October 2024. AuGroup (SHENZHEN) Cross-Border Business Co., Ltd. was incorporated in 2010 and is based in Shenzhen, China.", "Address": "Room 106, Kangli Information Valley Building, Shenzhen, China", "AddressData": {"Street": "Room 106, Kangli Information Valley Building", "City": "Shenzhen", "Country": "China"}, "Listings": {}, "Officers